# Contact Information — Sims Tech Only

This product is published by **Sims Tech** ([https://sims-service.com/](https://sims-service.com/)). All user-facing contact and support information must use only the official details from that site.

## Allowed

- **Email:** [vhlu@sims-service.com](mailto:vhlu@sims-service.com) (from the site contact)
- **Website:** https://sims-service.com/
- **Company name:** Sims Tech / SIMS tech
- **Product page:** https://sims-service.com/ (or the product subpath if applicable)

## Not allowed

- No other company or client emails (e.g. @sisn.com or other domains) in support/contact sections, README, release notes, or UI.
- No other support or contact URLs unless they point to sims-service.com.

## Where this applies

- UI (footer, About dialog, help text)
- README, docs, release notes (Support / Contact sections)
- Any new support or “contact us” text

When adding or editing support/contact text, use **vhlu@sims-service.com** and link to **https://sims-service.com/**.
